# Local testing scripts for dependency validation and bundle verification
# Files inside backend/scripts/local/ are local-only EXCEPT the bundle smoke test
# (used by release.sh — must be tracked). Pattern: ignore contents, then re-include.
# P0.9 (2026-05-15)
backend/scripts/local/*
!backend/scripts/local/test_bundle.py
bundle_test_results.json

